Imported into:   heterosplat / CUDA/Heterosplat/Source/Kernels/Thirdparty/Gsplat

Modifications applied during vendoring
--------------------------------------

Common.h
  - Removed PyTorch-coupled macros: CHECK_CUDA, CHECK_CONTIGUOUS, CHECK_INPUT,
    DEVICE_GUARD, CUB_WRAPPER. These reference TORCH_CHECK,
    at::cuda::OptionalCUDAGuard, and c10::cuda::CUDACachingAllocator and have
    no equivalents in our raw-pointer launcher path.
  - Kept: glm vec/mat typedefs, GAUSSIAN_EXTEND / MAX_ALPHA / TRANSMITTANCE_*
    constants, GSPLAT_NOINLINE.

Config.h
  - Unmodified.

Utils.cuh
  - Unmodified. Pure __device__ code, no torch dependency.

QuatScaleToCovarKernels.cuh (NEW)
  - Extracted the templated __global__ kernels
    quat_scale_to_covar_preci_{fwd,bwd}_kernel verbatim from gsplat's
    QuatScaleToCovarCUDA.cu. The launch_* host functions and AT_DISPATCH_*
    macro are dropped — replaced by raw-pointer launchers in
    CUDA/Heterosplat/Source/Kernels/Heterosplat/.

SphericalHarmonicsKernels.cuh (NEW)
  - Extracted the two __device__ helpers (sh_coeffs_to_color_fast and
    sh_coeffs_to_color_fast_vjp) and the two templated __global__ kernels
    spherical_harmonics_{fwd,bwd}_kernel verbatim from gsplat's
    SphericalHarmonicsCUDA.cu. The launch_* host functions and
    AT_DISPATCH_* macro are dropped.
  - Replaced ATen's gpuAtomicAdd (from <ATen/cuda/Atomic.cuh>) with the
    CUDA-native atomicAdd inside spherical_harmonics_bwd_kernel for the
    v_dirs accumulation. gpuAtomicAdd is a thin ATen wrapper around
    atomicAdd for the float case used here, so the substitution is
    bit-equivalent.

IntersectTileKernels.cuh (NEW)
  - Extracted the AccuTile/SNUGBOX device helpers and the templated
    intersect_tile_kernel from gsplat's IntersectTile.cu.
  - Dropped the ATen launch_intersect_tile_kernel host wrapper,
    AT_DISPATCH_FLOATING_TYPES dispatch, and CUB radix-sort helpers.
    heterosplat owns the raw-pointer launcher in
    CUDA/Heterosplat/Source/Kernels/Heterosplat/IntersectTile.cu and keeps
    sorting/prefix-sum storage explicit at the caller boundary.

IntersectOffsetKernels.cuh (NEW)
  - Extracted the __global__ intersect_offset_kernel from gsplat's
    IntersectTile.cu. This kernel converts sorted intersection ids into
    per-image/per-tile offsets.
  - Dropped the ATen launch_intersect_offset_kernel host wrapper.
    heterosplat owns the raw-pointer launcher in
    CUDA/Heterosplat/Source/Kernels/Heterosplat/IntersectOffset.cu.

ProjectionEWA3DGSFusedKernels.cuh (NEW)
  - Extracted the two templated __global__ kernels
    projection_ewa_3dgs_fused_fwd_kernel and
    projection_ewa_3dgs_fused_bwd_kernel from gsplat's
    ProjectionEWA3DGSFused.cu. The launch_* host functions,
    AT_DISPATCH_* macros, and the GSPLAT_BUILD_3DGS preprocessor guard
    are dropped — replaced by raw-pointer launchers in
    CUDA/Heterosplat/Source/Kernels/Heterosplat/ProjectionEWA3DGSFused.cu.
  - Replaced ATen's gpuAtomicAdd (from <ATen/cuda/Atomic.cuh>) with the
    CUDA-native atomicAdd in the backward kernel for gradient
    accumulation. gpuAtomicAdd is a thin ATen wrapper around atomicAdd
    for the float case used here, so the substitution is bit-equivalent.

Files NOT vendored from upstream
--------------------------------

  - QuatScaleToCovar.cpp / QuatScaleToCovar.h (torch boundary; replaced).
  - QuatScaleToCovarCUDA.cu's launch_* host functions (replaced).
  - Intersect.cpp / Intersect.h (torch boundary; replaced).
  - IntersectTile.cu's launch_* host functions and CUB radix-sort helpers
    (replaced by raw-pointer launchers).
  - 2DGS / 3DGUT / lidar / external-distortion / camera-wrappers kernels
    (out of scope for heterosplat — see PLAN.md done-criteria).

